    "TitleKey": "EckhartSecurity_EliminateBoss_DC_Title_001",
    "DisplayTitle": "High-Risk Bounty: [TargetName]",
    "Description": "ECKHART SECURITY, LLC.\nCONTRACTS & DISPATCH\n\nCONTRACT TYPE: Bounty\nAPPROVAL CODE = ~mission(ApprovalCode)\n\nFOR IMMEDIATE PROCESSING\n\nWe\u2019ve received actionable intelligence on a dangerous bounty, who\u2019s turned out to be extremely elusive. <EM4>~mission(TargetName)</EM4> was spotted with a dedicated contingent of known associates at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. We\u2019re looking for a contractor ready and willing to execute this bounty before they disappear again.\n\nBased on previous attempts to apprehend this criminal, there\u2019s a good chance that <EM4>~mission(TargetName|Last)</EM4> will try to avoid a direct confrontation, and instead send their allies to confront you. We believe that neutralizing these protective forces, and shredding the safety net they provide, is the best way to draw out <EM4>~mission(TargetName|Last)</EM4> to face you directly. \n\nExpect to confront a significant and skilled force. We advise that you plan accordingly. Payment will be issued upon successful completion of contract.\n\nThis contract is non-negotiable.\n\nThis message may contain confidential, proprietary, privileged and/or private information. The information is intended to be for the use of the individual or entity designated above.",
    "DescriptionKey": "EckhartSecurity_EliminateBoss_DC_Desc_001",
    "DisplayDescription": "ECKHART SECURITY, LLC.\nCONTRACTS & DISPATCH\n\nCONTRACT TYPE: Bounty\nAPPROVAL CODE = [ApprovalCode]\n\nFOR IMMEDIATE PROCESSING\n\nWe\u2019ve received actionable intelligence on a dangerous bounty, who\u2019s turned out to be extremely elusive. <EM4>[TargetName]</EM4> was spotted with a dedicated contingent of known associates at <EM4>Storehouse</EM4>. We\u2019re looking for a contractor ready and willing to execute this bounty before they disappear again.\n\nBased on previous attempts to apprehend this criminal, there\u2019s a good chance that <EM4>[TargetName|Last]</EM4> will try to avoid a direct confrontation, and instead send their allies to confront you. We believe that neutralizing these protective forces, and shredding the safety net they provide, is the best way to draw out <EM4>[TargetName|Last]</EM4> to face you directly. \n\nExpect to confront a significant and skilled force. We advise that you plan accordingly. Payment will be issued upon successful completion of contract.\n\nThis contract is non-negotiable.\n\nThis message may contain confidential, proprietary, privileged and/or private information. The information is intended to be for the use of the individual or entity designated above.",
